name: Grytpype and Moriarty Defence Authority Range
desc: Gives the top secret documents required to manufacture GMDA hulls, weapons and fighter chips. Looks like it was photographed while a nude Minister is holding it in front of his face.

name: Grytpype and Moriarty Stock Range
desc: A set of blueprints that enable the production of GM 'stock' ships. Does not include the more exclusive hulls.

name: GM Fire Service Range
desc: A set of blueprints that enable the production of GM Fire Service ships. Comes with associated designs for Louis Quinze fireman's furniture and marble statues of fire engines travelling at speed.

name: GM Health Service Range
desc: A set of blueprints that enable the production of GM Health Service ships. Comes with evidence of a doctor being unable to work for a national health service due to being on holiday on Eventide.
